{"title":"致举火炬者","authors":["程步涛"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":6,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致举火炬者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"程步涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的天空这样明亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是因为有无数举火炬者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在昨天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在阴霾比磐石还要沉重的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把自己也化作了火炬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们只顾着赶路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有火炬燃烧着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便向光明处奔跑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关隘闯过来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥淖走过来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们才看见过来的路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一座座石碑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是举火炬者燃烧的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，虽然阴霾已经消失"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但道路上仍然会出现泥泞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前方仍然会飘来浓雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举火炬者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然是光明的路标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们指明前途"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有高举火炬并甘愿燃烧自己的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一个民族的幸福"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}